        {
            "title": "搶救能源運輸 特朗普政府推200億美元油輪再保險計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"搶救能源運輸 特朗普政府推200億美元油輪再保險計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"597\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KehjJOZs.PD4gz55WKwryQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Nw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/708d70e0-19c7-11f1-bfff-0b4965fa52c5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">搶救能源運輸 特朗普政府推200億美元油輪再保險計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
